Package com.intellij.codeInspection

Interface CustomSuppressableInspectionTool

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseJavaLocalInspectionTool, CheckNodeTest, HardwiredNamespacePrefix, I18nInspection, ImplicitTypeConversion, IndexZeroPredicate, RedundantTypeConversion, TemplateInvocationInspection, UnusedElementInspection, VariableShadowingInspection, XPathInspection, XsltDeclarationInspection

    public interface CustomSuppressableInspectionTool
    This interface needs to be implemented by implementers of LocalInspectionTool and GlobalInspectionTool that support suppressing inspections.
